name: "Bathroom, mirror"
description:
"I know you´re the one who allowed the great dream to became true... the magnificence of that bathroom, the lights through the window, the cigarette, the mirror and your look, your white feet taking the right steps"

Video Montage - 2021.

This is the fourth "mini video" of a series of visual stories involving the "girl in the red dress" and myself, Lautaro Quiroga, as a character of this metaverse.

Girl in the red dress: Camila Pláate.
